{"tid":1743253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」陳奕迅演唱會取消！？","createTime":"2019-11-21T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:51:11.000Z","uid":162327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"523e427186a382db5577326bcdf294421b5051c5","tid":1743253,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"From 東網"},{"pid":"bceb1038266bb47c90ccdc29d470732e496bce28","tid":1743253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"link?無link即係fake news"},{"pid":"bff88025c98c3158345de357f0dada5bc7c8c872","tid":1743253,"uid":162327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WC6bXv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WC6bXv.png&h=fe4bc986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00a3edfc0b122f75b8bf2a5e19747ec9a89eac31","tid":1743253,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bceb1038266bb47c90ccdc29d470732e496bce28","tid":1743253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"link?無link即係fake news"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"補咗"},{"pid":"220359f731a47c2e82840b53ad259c98244db999","tid":1743253,"uid":42340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"eason唔想要港豬啲錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1745ae5c716fd1ed9758870e8680137ae942a3f8","tid":1743253,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"FWD富衛保險 陳奕迅 Fear and Dreams 香港演唱會 19/20<br />\n演出取消公告<br />\n<br />\n《FWD富衛保險 陳奕迅 Fear and Dreams 香港演唱會 19/20》是Eason闊別紅館六年後的首個香港大型演唱會，經連月籌備綵排，台前幕後已一切準備就緒，要將最精彩的演出呈獻給期待已久的樂迷。<br />\n<br />\n但鑒於近日情況，考慮到是次演唱會將於兩星期後舉行，我們實在無法預計和保證25場演出期間的觀衆安全和相關交通配套。經過與合作單位多番商議後，今天沉重宣布取消原定於紅磡香港體育館舉行的全部25場演唱會並將安排退票退款。<br />\n<br />\n這決定對我們來說是極為艱難。除了時間、心血、努力和經濟的損失，我們同時承受近二十萬名觀眾和歌手的失望和失落。由於涉及觀眾人數龐大、申請演唱會場地和演職人員檔期配合等問題複雜，請恕我們無法就改期演出作出承諾。<br />\n<br />\n原定於2019年11月25日起可提取經城市售票網公開發售門票的安排將會取消，已購票人士毋須前往提取門票。有關退票退款安排，我們與有關機構協商後，將於2019年12月18日於以下平台作出公佈，敬請留意：<br />\n<br />\n1） ESL Ltd Facebook專頁 (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/ESLLtdOfficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FESLLtdOfficial&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=d1dd5a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/ESLLtdOfficial</a>)<br />\n2） 陳奕迅官方網站 (<a href=\"http://www.easonchan.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.easonchan.net&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=a6b5595a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.easonchan.net</a>)<br />\n3） Universal Music Hong Kong Facebook 專頁 <br />\n(<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/UniversalMusicHongKong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUniversalMusicHongKong&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=2e216873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/UniversalMusicHongKong</a>)<br />\n4） UM Webzine Facebook 專頁 (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/umwebzine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fumwebzine&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=ef75f067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/umwebzine</a>)<br />\n5） 城市售票網網頁（<a href=\"http://www.urbtix.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.urbtix.hk&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=fc22055e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.urbtix.hk</a>）<br />\n6） 香港體育館網頁（<a href=\"http://www.lcsd.gov.hk/tc/hkc/index.html）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhkc%2Findex.html%EF%BC%89&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=8840a25f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.lcsd.gov.hk/tc/hkc/index.html）</a><br />\n<br />\n我們對是次取消深感歉意，請觀眾體諒。我們感激樂迷對Eason一直以來的支持。希望日後能夠再次成功申請紅館檔期，讓Eason在紅館為大家帶來更完美的演出。<br />\n<br />\n主辦機構：ESL Ltd<br />\n2019年11月21日"},{"pid":"3e01801442ce59bb60977ed0f28eb19e42710532","tid":1743253,"uid":323353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"等左咁耐最後都開唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116155aca2c03c1ead8a0f3171c3f932a3f05a25","tid":1743253,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"eason 表過態未？"},{"pid":"11942df2af92e455bafefa36484872d2dd7d0c0c","tid":1743253,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"116155aca2c03c1ead8a0f3171c3f932a3f05a25","tid":1743253,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"eason 表過態未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"一直唔關注"},{"pid":"aec76135b5f1bb0340f8bc78d56d3b29da3a1d1e","tid":1743253,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:28:39.000Z","msg":"多得紅隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e01c521bd2c1b539e82041fb1169b479fb19734","tid":1743253,"uid":162327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"116155aca2c03c1ead8a0f3171c3f932a3f05a25","tid":1743253,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"eason 表過態未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"窮願返大陸唱"},{"pid":"fc145c4ddee20eb3a9a87067dc0f589919aeb787","tid":1743253,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"又可以SPIN 黑警連累港豬冇EASON 睇"},{"pid":"938e20ccd9a779b54f5c168a76fae558d2f5c23d","tid":1743253,"uid":35107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:30:17.00